headline: Amcor: Fiscal Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: WARMLEY BRISTOL, Britain (AP) — Amcor plc (AMCR) on Wednesday reported fiscal third-quarter earnings of $196 million. On a per-share basis, the Warmley Bristol, Britain-based company said it had net income of 14 cents. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, were 18 cents per share.
